		<div id="comment_body_65483942"><p>I use LLMs for my own amusement, they are useful for that.</p><p>I have little to no visual memory so I struggle to draw even simple things. I can do drafting-style sketches OK because they are logical, but just remembering the shape of a curve even between looking at the thing and looking at the paper is difficult. So I use AI to generate images and feel zero remorse about it, since it lets me do something I cannot otherwise do &mdash; envision a concept I can imagine, but cannot picture.</p><p>For answering questions,<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
