	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65483968"><p>I use it much like a community to get help with programming, asking questions such as "what does this statement do?" or "what are ways to do X?"  or "What is wrong with this code<nobr> <wbr></nobr>...?" or " Can I accomplish X by doing this using this code...? I don't use it to simply 'vibe code' but to help me get over a hurdle when I can't figure something out; much like how a community works but with instant response.</p><p>I view it as an adjunct and learning tool; not to simply produce cut and paste code.  If it generates code<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

