The last time I thought, let's see if Chatgpt has some extra suggestions on the topic. I gave it the text of my presentation. It answered, "your presentation is already reasonably well structured, and I will make the text flow a bit better" -  being not native English I appreciated the edits; and then it suggested some extra slides as I had asked. I checked with chatgpt and using google on these; and found them niche yet quite well</div>
